name: In Her World
description: In her world there is darkness you are not familiar with; there are shadows all around you; skirts are falling, you cannot see your way clear. There are secrets you cannot recall, and there are the things yonder just a bit too close to be missed. You seem to lose yourself in the world, and that's something I fear more than being trapped. I see shadows of myself in you, my darling, and I can't help it. I wish I could hide from you.
